---
title: About — Claudio Vallejo
meta_title: About
description: Hi there! I’m Claudio, a Mexican web designer and front-end developer freelancing from Monterrey, Mexico. At the moment I’m looking for a job opportunity in the United States as a Product Designer working on design systems or business tools with global impact.
---
<%# Config %>
<% about = data.about %>
<%# Content %>
<main>
  <div class="mw8-l center mt4-m">
    <div class="cf">
      <div class="fl-ns w-10-m w-20-l" style="min-height: 1px;"></div>
      <div class="fl-ns w-80-m w-60-l">
        <%# Hero %>
        <article class="mb4">
          <div class="aspect-ratio aspect-ratio--1x1 aspect-ratio aspect-ratio--16x9-ns">
            <div class="aspect-ratio--object cover bg-center" title="Hola! Mucho gusto, soy Claudio :)" style="background-image: url(images/portrait-dark.jpg)"></div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="ph1 ph0-ns">
          <%# Bio %>
          <%# Variables %>
          <% bsl = about.bio.content.length - 1 %>
          <%# End %>
          <h3 class="ma0 mb2 lato f075 tracked ttu gray"><%= about.bio.title %></h3>
          <%# end %>
          <% about.bio.content.each_with_index do |section, s| %>
            <p class="ma0 <% if s != bsl %>mb2<% else %>mb4<% end %> merriweather dark-gray lh-copy"><%= section %></p>
          <% end %>
          <div class="cf">
            <%# Detail Sections %>
            <%# Variables %>
            <% dsl = about.details.length - 1 %>
            <%# End %>
            <% about.details.each_with_index do |section, s| %>
              <div class="fl-ns w-50-ns <% if s != dsl %>mb4<% end %>">
                <h3 class="ma0 mb2 lato f075 tracked ttu gray"><%= section.title %></h3>
                <ul class="ma0 merriweather pa0 list">
                  <%# Details %>
                  <%# Variables %>
                  <% dll = section.content.length - 1 %>
                  <% section.content.each_with_index do |detail, d| %>
                    <li class="<% if d != dll %>mb2<% end %>">
                      <a class="mb05 dib no-underline dark-gray dim" href="<%= detail.source %>" target="_blank"><%= detail.title %></a>
                      <p class="ma0 gray"><%= detail.subtitle %></p>
                    </li>
                  <% end %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="fl-ns w-10-m w-20-l" style="min-height: 1px;"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
